notification-bundle-header-page-connecti:
Bundled message for the page connection notification. Parameters:
* $1 – formatted username of the person who connected the first page
* $2 – raw username of the person who connected the first page, for GENDER support
* $3 – title of the first page that was connected
* $4 – the number of other pages that were connected, except that if the count is greater than 99, this value will be 100; uses standard number formatting and used for PLURAL
See also:
* {{msg-mw|Notification-header-page-connection}}
* {{msg-mw|Notification-bundle-header-page-linked}}
{{Related|Notification-bundle}}

